channel.description: OK i got Moparscape with Aryan and all that. I got Hamachi also. Once that is done, I always try to log in and it gives me a message saying that the server is in timed out or something like that. I've tried this like 5 differant times now and it keeps happening. Am I doing something wrong? If I am, please take the time to explain to me how to do this. Thank you!
